**False leg found on slime molds, archaea, protozoans, leukocytes and certain bacteria**

This article is about [eukaryotic](/Eukaryotic) cells. For the band, see [Pseudopod (band)](/Pseudopod_(band)). For the podcast, see [Pseudopod (podcast)](/Pseudopod_(podcast)). For the structure in insect anatomy, see [Proleg](/Proleg).

